      "title": "Pixaroma - Note - START HERE (Episode Nunchaku)",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# !!! This workflow is made for COMFYUI-Nunchaku Version\n\n### Install this portable ComfyUI version into a different folder following the instructions from [HERE](https://github.com/Tavris1/ComfyUI-Easy-Install/tree/Windows-Nunchaku)\n\n# Works only with Nvidia Card and Windows\n\n---\n\n## 🟣 Nunchaku FLUX DiT Loader\n### Download svdq-int4_r32-flux.1-kontext-dev.safetensors from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/mit-han-lab/nunchaku-flux.1-kontext-dev/resolve/main/svdq-int4_r32-flux.1-kontext-dev.safetensors?download=true)\n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models` \n\nMore Info about the model [HERE](https://huggingface.co/mit-han-lab/nunchaku-flux.1-kontext-dev/tree/main)\n\n---\n\n## 🟣 Nunchaku Text Encoder Loader V2\n\n###  Download clip_l.safetensors from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/comfyanonymous/flux_text_encoders/resolve/main/clip_l.safetensors?download=true)  \n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/clip`  \n\n###  Download awq-int4-flux.1-t5xxl.safetensors from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/mit-han-lab/nunchaku-t5/resolve/main/awq-int4-flux.1-t5xxl.safetensors?download=true)\n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/clip`\n\n---\n\n## 🟣 Load VAE\n\n### Download **ae.safetensor** vae model from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Lumina_Image_2.0_Repackaged/resolve/main/split_files/vae/ae.safetensors?download=true)  \n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/vae`  \n\n---\n\n## 🆙 Load Upscale Model  \n\n### Download 4x_NMKD-Siax_200k.pth mode from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Akumetsu971/SD_Anime_Futuristic_Armor/resolve/main/4x_NMKD-Siax_200k.pth?download=true)  \n\n**Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/upscale_models`\n\n---\n\n## 📚 Resources  \n🎥 **Tutorials:** [Pixaroma YouTube Channel](https://www.youtube.com/@pixaroma)  \n💬 **Community Discord:** [Join Here](https://discord.com/invite/gggpkVgBf3)\n\nLearn more about Kontext model on [Comfy.org](https://docs.comfy.org/tutorials/flux/flux-1-kontext-dev) and [blf.ai](https://bfl.ai/models/flux-kontext)\n\nLearn how to prompt for Flux Kontext [HERE](https://docs.comfy.org/tutorials/flux/flux-1-kontext-dev#flux-kontext-prompt-techniques)\n\nLearn more about Nunchaku [HERE](https://github.com/mit-han-lab/ComfyUI-nunchaku)\n"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
